** devops 5th one **:

LINK:https://pdfhost.io/v/B5ERPaAP3n_DEVOPS-LAB-P5

download maven binary zip
set environment variable to bin

setx MAVEN_HOME "your path" /M
setx PATH "%PATH%;YOUR BIN PATH" /M

mvn -v (to check running)
mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.example -DartifactId=demo-project -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart -DinteractiveMode=false (create project)

to pom.xml add:
<dependency>
<groupId>com.google.code.gson</groupId>
<artifactId>gson</artifactId>
<version>2.10.1</version>
</dependency>

cd demo-project

mvn compile
mvn test
mvn package

java -cp target/demo-project1-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.example.App

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**for 6th continue with**:
LINK: https://pdfhost.io/v/YAJNdBn7cD_DEVOPS-LAB-Program6


- delete pom.xml

- download gradle

setx GRADLE_HOME "YOUR PATH" /M
setx PATH "%PATH%; <PATH TO GRADLE BIN>" M\

gradle -v

make two gradle files:
build.gradle:

plugins {
id 'java'
}
group = 'com.example'
version = '1.0-SNAPSHOT'
repositories {
mavenCentral()
}
dependencies {
testImplementation'junit:junit:4.13.2'
}


settings.gradle:
rootProject.name='demo-project1'

gradle build 
gradle test

java -cp build/libs/demo-project1-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.example.App 
java -cp target/demo-project1-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.example.App (backup)

